{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"602","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"巴拿馬運河面臨缺水危機","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-01-03 02:10 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報 編譯易起宇／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>巴拿馬政府<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>31</span>日紀念巴拿馬運河移交<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>周年，但這條運河現在卻面臨著威脅其存續的缺水危機。降雨減少和氣溫升高，已導致為運河船閘注入水源的淡水湖水位下降。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>雖然巴拿馬政府自<span lang='EN-US'>1999</span>年底從美國手中接下運河管理權以來，在營運和業務擴張一直很順遂，但現在卻面臨了一項新挑戰：為運河船閘尋找新水源。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>巴拿馬運河管理當局早在數月前就已實施水深限制，限制使用這條水路貨輪的載運量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>氣候變遷和近來為容納更大船隻通行所進行的擴建，可能使這座<span lang='EN-US'>105</span>年歷史的運河設計面臨嚴重考驗。為這座運河開鑿的人工湖「加通湖」，不只提供船隻運行的功能，也供應巴國約一半的飲用水。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>發電水壩專家布蘭登表示：「這座運河水域上游的降雨不足以維持目前擴建後運河的繼續營運，更不用說再進一步擴建。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6812/4264548?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-03","clk_count":"118"}},"__N_SSG":true}